    "2846175354201753542007/10/26 21:39:39shammanIf it all goes wrong when pulling Velratha (or any mobs in this part of ZF) your party can jump into the pool and swim down into the deep end. Eventually they'll lose interest and you can heal up and try again.\
\
Another spell of note that Velratha casts is Shadow Bolt Volley - it hit me as a lvl49 mage for around 400hp so try to have a mage or shaman or whatever counterspell/interrupt it. I didn't see whether or not the volley was directed at myself only or the party as a whole, sorry.",
