    "6610205036102050362007/12/21 11:49:55CeliceIf you are Alliance and are power-levelling fishing and cooking in parallel, you will need to do this quest once you have reached level 225 by fishing [i]Mithril Head Trout[/i] from outside Stromgarde Keep. Before travelling to Tanaris to pick up this quest, get everything you need to complete it from [b]The Hinterlands[/b] just around the corner:\
