    "6610119410281885862007/07/12 06:20:03WirelessEasy way of doing this quest without having to leave Tanaris:\
\
<< Giant Egg >>\
Venture south, out of Gadgetzan and head towards one of the various giant rib cages (47, 43 - around here and further south) sticking out of the sand. Kill any bird-type mobs that hang around. The Giant eggs drop off these at a very good drop rate.\
\
<< Zesty Clam Meat >>\
Head east from Gadgetzan right to the coast, up to steamwheedle port. (66, 23) Kill the numerous turtles there. These mobs will drop clams which have the meat inside that you need. Simply right click on the clams in your backpack to open them.\
\
<< Alterac Swiss >>\
Head South-East from Gadgetzan towards the Cavern of Times (61, 50) Talk to the dragon inside just past the summoning stone and get a ride to the bottom. (Not sure what levels can do this, if you can't - just ride down.) Once you land, turn around and start heading back the way you came and you should see a tower with two NPCs outside. Talk to the NPC orc on the inside and he will sell you the cheese. (If you had to ride down, keep heading downwards until you see a tower on your left with the two NPCs outside)\
\
Once this is done, you should have all of your quest items and be ready to hand it in. Head back to Gadgetzan Inn and get your next level in cooking.",
