\
- Everytime you open the chest the loot changes. I noticed this accidently. When I first got the chest, it had some silver, two green items (one was a lvl 45 \"...of the Bear\" type mail leggings), and two grey items inside (two maces). I did not have space in my bags so I kept the items inside the chest and hearthed to IF. In IF, I emptied my bags and opened the chest again to get the items - and what do you know? I still had two grey and green items but they had changed to head band (greys) and \"...of the something other than Bear\" leather pants. The other one was a recipe. Sorry I do not remember what it was previouosly. \
