The best way to get this book is to enter the north dire maul instance. Once inside, go into cat form and stealth, walk left and go down the slope where you will see wandering dogs, and the ogre boss. Stay away from the dogs, they can see you in stealth. Now, when you get to the bottom, stealth left and you will see a locked door, this is where you can enter with your crescent key. Once inside follow the hallway to a room and you will see elven NPC's. The quest npc you seek is in this room and you can talk to him to complete. Congrats you have your trinket!",
