    "2770200438102004382007/12/12 23:44:50SeraRavenOn this date, a group of a 45 Mage (myself), a 45 Rogue, a 44 Warrior and a 52 Shaman managed to get through here. Three of us had the mallet and all four of us had the quest. However, when Gah`zrilla died only the group leader (45 Rogue) got the scale. Is this some sort of new glitch from the patch? One would think something like this would be a group loot........Not that I mind killing the guy four times, he drops some pretty good loot.\
