    "48662031161133502007/01/12 03:14:19NimchipAlso make sure nobody cleanses you or anything of the like.. I did this quest and upon porting to IF, a paladin thought it might be helpful if he removed my poison. Needless to say, I failed the quest.",
    "4866177625201776252007/11/01 08:04:16novemberYes, it is still possible to solo the quest as a rogue this way. I just did. \
