otherwise, just kill caliph straightaway, and run - the rogues wouldnt stay on your tail for long. after that return and loot his head.",
    "2781210167111249982007/12/30 23:40:01Outlaw73Another warrior trick, or any class with a fear move is to go all out and kill Caliph first, loot his head, then fear the remaining guards and book outta there.",
