    "43221032550103252006/12/08 00:50:24DSitCSince this is one of the most time consuming escort quests in the game (due to a lot of trash clearing) make absolutely sure that everyone in your group has completed the Quest \"A Shred of Hope\" (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4282) before starting this one. Once the event is running, it can only be started anew by resetting the instance and clearing all the trash again, afaik.\
\
