    "4322207160211606172007/12/25 17:10:32coyote72100 runs and he's always gone one way, if you're coming in from the center room, he'll exit through the right side, but mobs will spawn and you will have to face small bosses on the way, that's why he does not go either way. Out of the jail cell, he will turn left.",
