    "428215852npcMarshal Windsor9023npcMarshal Windsor90236200Stormwind2501426424282",
    "428211034100110342006/12/08 12:17:13LittlefangThis quest is the prereq for Jail Break! (http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4322) and the final step before escorting Windsor out of Blackrock Depths and into Stormwind. When turning this quest in, do NOT take the follow up (Jail Break!) because it will start the escort part of the quest. Either keep the items until you get a group for Jail Break! and warn them ahead of time you haven't turned it in yet, or turn in the items and do not hit \"accept\" to the next quest.\
