    "4282179261101792612007/11/04 19:01:03frostymageGeneral Angerforge: He's in the West Garrison. Assuming you have the Shadowforge Key, from where you enter BRD, open the gate north, then open the first gate along the right wall, and open the East Garrison door. You'll be in a room with a mechanism. Kill all the mobs in the room, then use the mechanism. Head upstairs and clear left until you reach a hallway with windows overlooking the Dark Iron Highway. The bridge on the other side should be open, so cross it and enter West Garrison. Angerforge is downstairs on the left from where you enter the garrison.\
