    "815393151093152006/12/07 18:43:13blackironFor this and the Wave Trasher quest after, go for the higher level mobs.  In the case of these, the coursers, focus exclusively on the level 53 coursers.  The levels of the coursers are not evenly dispersed.  The stretch extending northwest from the blue dragons contains primarily level 52 coursers.  You find more concentrated level 53 coursers by heading east or northeast, but watch out for the giants.  It will still take a long time, but more like 30 minutes instead of two hours.",
