[Ring of Protection] or [Archlight Talisman] or [Magebane Scion]\
\
Good luck to you and I hope all goes well!\
Also if this was helpful to you please rate it up.  TY!\
\
~Tessalyn, Dragonblight server",
    "5168132539101325392007/08/05 09:02:15SushilashThere were two Paladins in the first little room, one in the second room and two in the room where the Libram is. I ran inside to the end of the room, died, ran back and ressed. I scorched one of the Paladins so i would aggro, i froze them got the book and ran out.",
