    "51685524470552442007/03/22 07:20:45tntiseverywereIf you are lucky in the same room with Davil's Libram you will find Scarlet Judge... a rare spawn :)",
    "516870333070332006/12/06 06:01:47dsrboThe libram is in the house looking like the Southshore Inn, first floor, inner room, on a table. It glows.\
\
