    "2879211968102119682008/01/03 02:35:53entropicdragonThe names of the four flames appear to be a reference to the names of the four [url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cross-quarter_day]cross-quarter days[/url] (days halfway between solstice and equinox) in pagan culture:\
