    "3372169673101696732007/10/16 09:00:43SavvycatSoloed as a lvl 51 shadow priest. Killing the elites wasn't that difficult (for my class), but took a decent amount of time and a lot of mana for each one. I had to eat and drink after each pull. I couldn't kill all the mobs around the lava in time, since they respawn very fast. When I was almost about to give up as I ran out of food, I got the mobs around the lava down to one. I mind-soothed this mob and hoped for the best. Luckily I was able loot the artifact without agroing the mob. I wouldn't recommend this to be soloed around this level, unless you know that you can take down the elites quickly and without mistakes.",
    "3372167172101671722007/10/13 04:13:27ChaoticDescentIs there any way to reset the idolaters aggroing you after they do it the first time? That buggy one on the south-west corner aggroed when I attacked a mob over there, and now I can't get near the damned thing. I tried to kill off the idolaters one by one, but they're chain-aggroing now.",
