    "4284350635035062006/11/12 02:40:50ollitropInitially you must turn in seven of each color crystal (red, blue, yellow and green) at the end of the cave right by the camp/fly point in Un'Goro. You will be given a book which will allow you to receive items from the spires. You will need 10 each of 2 colors to collect a Crystal. \
