    "8185166022101660222007/10/11 14:38:47ninjasuperspyThe question is: would this be a better tanking head enchant than the KoT Revered glyph?  The consensus on the Warrior version ([url=http://wowhead.com/?item=19782]Presence of Might[/url]) appears to be that by virtue of its Stam, the PoM beats the Glyph of the Defender.\
\
