    "8185153039111453752007/09/14 17:38:21kapowazSpellthread is a much better option for leg items. For head items, there is the Glyph of Renewal ([url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29189]Alliance[/url] / [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29190]Horde[/url]) which offers vastly superior healing and MP5.",
    "8185145375101453752007/08/28 09:31:36WarMasterI haven't been able to get a ZG group together on my server yet.  Does anyone know if this quest is still Alliance only in BC, or can Horde Paladins now obtain it?",
