    "8185184995111660222007/11/15 09:50:59leonheart87Bloodlord Mandokir is 2-mannable (in kara gear). Just did it with a paladin and a warrior. Took 40minutes roughly, but overall it was a pretty easy fight - the bugger didn't drop a mount though :(",
