    "76034589711143302007/03/04 06:28:01mizoreJust soloed at 52. I'm afflition speced. I just kept imp out, feared, and kept dots up. Used Dark Pact on imp when low on mana. Only had to use one HS and one bandaid. Only took a few minutes.",
    "7603157454101574542007/09/24 04:23:41fbg111Solo'd as lvl 55  5/41/0 Demo lock.  ~2500 base health, 3000 buffed with several pots and scrolls (very nice pot from Blood Elf quest givers in Blasted Lands, gives +25 stam for 1hr), ~200 spell dmg (shadow & generic, including Wizard Oil on my sword).\
\
Succubus on passive for MD +10% dmg, Soul Link for 5% dmg and mitigation (she's fragile, but only got down to about 1/2 health).  Fear + CoS + Corr + Drain Life, repeat as necessary.  CoS instead of CoA to decrease Fear resists and early breaks.  Banished and bandaged once, used health stone and one Greater Healing Pot.\
\
So it is possible for full Demo locks to do this, even with limited dots.  My spec:  http://www.wowhead.com/?talent=IVZbxczIizcesz\
