I also wonder if it's possible to enslave the elite Infernals walking around the scar, there are some lvl 53 and 54, and use one of them to kill Kroshius, similar to using the ones in Nagrand to solo the group quests there.  That was going to be my next strategy if the first didn't work, but didn't get to try it.",
    "7603179631101796312007/11/05 14:02:37caskeperWould just like to add that he aggros mobs he runs past, when in combat. Had a resist on my curse of recklessness when it was running towards one of those normal elements around there, so my first attempt to solo it at 51 failed. Second didn't cause too much hassle though.",
