    "7603156847301568472007/09/22 21:36:36LevelelevenAfter I completed this quest Niby summoned something he wanted to be an infernal. What he got was El Pollo Grande, a \"Black chicken of death\", quoting from it's description. It was a giant chicken that attacked me, only a level 50 so it was nothing serious. That event was actually quite amusing.",
