    "7603153077101530772007/09/14 19:28:09JaedxRaptureJust soloed this as a 53 affliction lock (http://www.wowhead.com/?talent=IVMriRfzVtbo0h ) with 240 shadow damage and 3.3k health (with imp out). Took a long time but wasn't at all *hard*. Here's what I did:\
\
As soon as he rose, spam fear. He won't become hostile immediately so keep hitting it till you see it begin to cast. As soon as he begins running get ALL DoTs up, including UA and Siphon Life, and keep them up. Keep fear up, and if he resists it use Death Coil or instant Howl of Terror to give you time to recast. Make sure you keep DoTs reapplied. And do not try drain tanking, as he's just too hard for that.\
\
Didn't have to use any bandages, stones, etc etc for it. After a while my Imp ran out of mana for Dark Pact, but Life Tap + Drain Life was just as easy.\
