on other hand, you can nuke him down fast we got him to 7% with just a crappy gear hunter (70)  and me (60 pala) but called for a 70 mage to come and help : )\
\
Edit: That is on the Step 5: Ancient Equine Spirit part in DM",
    "7637210163111904582007/12/30 23:33:09SoulcatcherI disagree with sotiseb and Daleus' comments.  The paladin and warlock mount quest chains are two of the most fun (at level) quest lines in the entire game.  Yes, if grinding to level 70 as fast as possible is your goal, by all means skip it.  But if you like the game for all of its content, and not just for the endgame reputation/equipment grind, this quest, and the warlock epic mount quest, should not be missed.",
