    "276682222082222006/12/07 03:42:32enasimaSoloed this as a 46 mage actually. The main problem is getting from the cave to the road.. generally a bear or ape will agro as the three yeti that spawn about 30m from the road attack, which can make for a very tough fight. The other spawns(gorillas followed by some gnolls) are easier to deal with ~ not much worry of outside agro either.",
    "27666393320639332007/04/08 15:16:37JohnJSalI'm going to post this message on all three of these \"Find\" quests, just in case someone doesn't see it on one of the other two.\
