Truthfully, while leveling my lock up to level 58 right now, I have only ever been short on shards once (though I have never ran out of shards).\
\
Knowing all that, I picked the weapon simply because I can look cool while walking around town with it. I suspect if I had taken the trinket that it would be gathering dust in my inventory or bank.\
\
Really, if you're that critically low on shards that often, to make having this trinket even an issue, I think you'd seriously have to examine your playstyle.",
