    "448422187022182006/10/24 13:50:06jasonThis is actually quite useful for a paladin.  Consider what the +8 Int does for us.  First, +8 Int.  Assuming at 60 the paladin formula for spell crit is:\
\
[INT/29.5?]%\
\
