\
Now, also assume that paladins have Divine Intellect, and Blessing of Kings, that increases the 8 int to about 9.6 (or 9.68, however, they do the math) int.  Assuming they round up, that's 10 int.\
\
Compare this to the ZG enchant, which give us 10 Stamina, 24 healing, and 7 defense.  Assuming at this point that defense is all but useless for a current end-game raiding paladin, it comes down to +healing and stamina and more mana and spell crit.\
\
