    "4484180575111445102007/11/07 13:44:18TenjouFor demo locks, Voracity (+8 STA) is a much better choice than Constitution (+100 HP).\
\
5/5 Demonic Embrace will raise your STA gained by 15% -- 9.2 STA. That will be equal to 90 or 100 HP, depending on the rounding with the rest of your gear.\
\
In addition to the 90/100 HP:\
\
+ Your pet's STA will be based off of a percentage of your STA, not your HP.\
+ The percentage of +9.2 STA going toward your pet will be increased by another 15% with 3/3 Fel Stamina -- a percentage of +10.58 STA.\
+ And then a percentage of this increase in STA will be added by 3/3 Demonic Knowledge as an increase to spell damage based off of 15% of your pet's total STA and INT.\
\
+8 STA is vastly superior to +100 HP. Equivalent HP gain, more HP for your pet, and more +spell dmg for you.\
\
