    "380216106540161062006/12/15 22:47:38mauriceHere's how you get to Fineous:\
\
1) Go into BRD (duh).\
\
2) Go straight, clear your way to the path directly in front of you- this is the path that runs almost perfectly east/west along the southern side of the Arena.\
\
