Once you enter this area, you'll see two exits on the right hand wall, take the last one and you'll find the golem room.\
\
It isn't exactly a straight shot to him.  \
\
The fight with him was pretty easy as I solo'd with a lvl 69 demo warlock, but he still gave me a run for my money.  He can heal himself and he has a lot of starting health.",
