  ["Craftsman's Writ60"] = {
    "914260npcDispatch Commander Metz16212npcDispatch Commander Metz16212Argent Dawn10",
    "9142114687101146872007/07/02 23:23:02fatherdougalWhat everyone here is glossing over is that not only do you get Argent Dawn rep (albeit a small amount), you also get your choice of insignia: http://www.wowhead.com/?item=22524 or http://www.wowhead.com/?item=22523 . \
