    "7641195202201952022007/12/03 02:58:52enchantrollSeriously... I can understand these quests in WoW version 1.  But how does Blizzard expect paladins to get GROUPS for these instances in the Burning Crusade era?  (Not to mention with another expansion a few months away).  Dire Maul?  Stratholme?  Scholomance?  I could be trying in vain for literally weeks on my server to get a group to run these.\
