    "763460npcHastat the Ancient14526npcHastat the Ancient145269950",
    "763467775067772006/12/05 21:42:02UrogThe Mature Blue Dragon Sinew used to make this quiver drops from Azuregos (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6109), The Cobalt Scalebanes in Mazthoril, Winterspring (http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18704) or a friendly guildmate. If your guild can easily take down Azuregos, I suggest not farming endless hours in Mazthoril. If you have extra gold floating around, these seem to go anywhere from 80g to 800g.",
    "7634124474201244742007/07/21 10:59:42dainer09Even to this day after the release of the expansion, this is the best out there, only tied by http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29143 for the horde and http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29144 for the alliance. Now, its a lot easier to obtain the one from your Nagrand faction, but if you ever come across the Mature Blue Dragon Sinew, I would sugest to try and sell it, but you may not have the best of luck with it since its easier to obtain these, so really, its all up to you.\
\
~Lerex",
    "7634127750201277502007/07/27 12:26:33Jivocan you only get the quiver if you have the leaf from mc?\
because i thought about getting the quiver for style reasons (i got the one from the mag'har wich is as good as the epic one) but i never had the leaf.",
    "7634163967701639672007/10/06 21:22:08RazielI just finished this quest today. It was quite a pain to figure out how to get this quest. Here's what you need to do:\
\
1.) Go to Molten Core and get the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18703]Ancient Petrified Leaf[/url] from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?object=179703]Cache of the Firelord[/url].\
2.) Right click the leaf to start [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=7632]The Ancient Leaf[/url] quest.\
3.) Turn the quest in at [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=14524]Vartrus the Ancient[/url] in Felwood.\
4.) Now speak with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=14526]Hastat the Ancient[/url] (he's right next to Vartrus the Ancient) and get the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=7634]Ancient Sinew Wrapped Lamina[/url] quest.\
5.) Go to Azshara and kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6109]Azuregos[/url].\
6.) Loot [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18704]Mature Blue Dragon Sinew[/url] from Azuregos.\
7.) Return to Hastat the Ancient with the Mature Blue Dragon Sinew to finish the quest. Upon completion you will recieve the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=18714]Ancient Sinew Wrapped Lamina[/url] quiver.\
\
Notes: Obviously the hardest parts of this quest line are getting the Ancient Petrified Leaf and killing Azuregos.\
\
Good luck.",
    "76341484660148462006/12/13 13:13:07trannsvaalAs I have said in another comment, quivers are not to be underestimated. This is the best quiver in-game by now\
(pre-expansion). Apart from giving you 15% ranged attack speed (yeah only ranged, why are you meleeing???) it also provides you with 18 slots to put in 3600 arrows of your choice. Now 3600 arrows may seem too much, but if you are venturing to a new instance with your guild, meaning a lot of wipes you will need the arrows cause you can't be back and forth to the nearest town to buy arrows,",
    "7634130648211277502007/08/01 18:35:10FatnubYep, this quest is only obtainable if you have the leaf.",
