    "84181611310161132006/12/15 23:03:32spideywspI made the mistake of choosing the ring when I completed this quest.  The +7 str/sta/int and healing bonus looked nice to me at the time, but now that I am 60 it's obsolete.  If I could choose again I would definitely pick the trinket.  Trinket bonuses never seem to get replaced as you progress in levels.",
    "84186240021526772007/04/05 07:09:58defektungeYou'll replace that trinket within a few levels of entering outlands, as there are plenty of excellent quest reward trinkets around for every build. With TBC released, there's no real reason to put that much thought into what reward you choose from this quest. Just go with whatever you're going to use, or just pick the sword and sell it. You'll have replaced all of these long before you hit 70 anyway.",
    "84181571420157142006/12/15 00:40:48madedogThe Holy Mightstone is the only such item you can get, so choose carefully where you use it.\
