    "13602568510256852007/01/27 11:38:41foojo1Taken from Allakhazam\
\
It is definitely outside of the instance. If you go in through the 'front entrance' it will be in the bottom-leftmost room on the minimap. The treasure is inside of a small chest in a room full of troggs.",
    "1360105439201054392007/06/16 12:33:05UthersPrincessTried to solo as 46 holy priest... Ended up dying and rezzing multiple times, ultimately ending up in the room but my armor was garbage...but I did complete it. To get there, take front entrance and go along path as if going to instance, but keep straight. There will be a fork, keep left. As soon as you go left you will see to your left shadowforges and to your right the stonevault troggs. Go where the troggs are (most lvl 36-37 elite). Fight (or sneak) through into North Common Hall. Chest will be in southwest corner of first room- where there is a blob of rocks on the minimap. There are 3 troggs in hall leading to the room and 6 troggs in the room. If careful you can probably pull to fight one at a time. Good luck.",
    "13601080721601080722007/06/20 15:36:19Lieandra1. Enter Uldaman's front entrance.\
\
2. Walk in and the screen will show you enter \"Excavation Center\", continue forward and go under tunnel.\
\
3. Screen will show you back in \"Uldaman\". Continue forward and screen will show you in \"Dig One\". Upon entering \"Dig One\", follow the path left. Do not jump off the edge to the instance portal.\
\
4. At the first fork in the road. Go left and screen will show you again in \"Uldaman\". As the word \"Uldaman\" pops up; you are again in a fork on the road. Left = Dwarves  -*-  Right = Troggs. Go right towards the Troggs.\
\
5. Continue forward and the screen shows you enter \"North Common Hall\".\
6. Go through the tiled hallway, and when you enter the room; go towards the far wall in-front of you. Then look towards the right, and the chest is there on the floor.\
\
*Note: Standing on the box. I have these coordinates: 53,62.\
\
*Note: I put a picture here showing the box location, and some tips for rogues looking to solo this quest.\
\
~Lie",
