    "5242180880101808802007/11/08 04:38:31Ratix0This quest is quite easy... I managed it as a level 53 demonology speced warlock. Was doing the extinguish flame quest, went through the dungeon, cleared the succubus before and these 3, then realised that this is part of the quest after the one i was clearing. So... I had to clear it again ._.\
\
Overall if you're a warlock, get felguard and it should be a piece of cake. Banish the level 54 succubus, focus fire on the shadow lord, then kill the level 54 succubus after shes got out of her banish then clear the level 52 succubus. Make sure u clear the surroundings to prevent adds, and fear helps abit. Be careful though, the succubus can charm you to make u attack ur pet for about 5 seconds.",
    "5242202409102024092007/12/16 15:08:21DrasanThis quest was exceedingly easy with a 56 mage.\
