    "614396742039672006/11/21 13:38:26OrmrissTo find Gorlash, leave Booty Bay from the tunnel, then head to the east coast.  You should pass through an area with Bloodsail mages/swashbucklers.  As soon as you hit the beach, start running north.  You should see Gorlash walking around in the ocean (he's huge and hard to miss).\
