    "2681188572101885722007/11/20 21:20:19StevegasmI've leveled up a lot of 60+s, and every time I did this quest, it was bugged, but doable.  Today, I can say that it did not bug for me.  I did not test out the theory whether or not being close or far from the stone makes any difference, but just to be safe, I killed the servants of razilikh close to their stones anyway.",
    "26811132151501132152007/06/30 04:48:41shadedarkanHere is everything you need to know:\
\
Soloed as a 54 Warlock.\
\
Servants of Grol are level 53-54:\
\
Two at Dreadmaul Hold 43,13(inside gate, outside cave)\
Surrounding Mobs are level 46-47.\
\
Enter the gate and attack to the right. The servant on the right side has 3 mobs next to his stone situated in the middle of the catapults on the left. The servant hides in the roots of the large tree past his stone with one mob standing next to him. Proceed around the back to the other side of the cave. The second servant's stone, situated just before the catapults on the left, has 4 mobs next to it. The servant hides next to the large tree past his stone on the right (you can't see him there if you enter the gate and attack to the left) with one mob near him.\
\
One in Dreadmaul Post 49,43\
Surrounding mobs are level 55-57.\
Over 10 mobs at entrance.\
\
I did as recommended above and waited for a respawn at Dreadmaul Hold rather than try to get in here.\
\
Servants of Sevine are level 56:\
\
Along the path to the Alter of Storms 39,32\
Surrounding mobs are level 53-55.\
3-5 mobs around the servant at base of path.\
1 mob near servant mid-way along path.\
1 mob near servant at top of path.\
\
Servants of Alistarj are level 55:\
\
Along the Eastern border from Serpent's Coil South\
65,32 \
Surrounding mobs are level 51-53.\
4 mobs near servant's crystal.\
\
64,40\
Surrounding mobs are level 52-53.\
2 mobs near servan'ts crystal.\
\
64,46\
Surrounding mobs are level 52-53.\
4 mobs around servant's crystal.\
\
I could not pull this servant's mobs individually due to their close proximity to the servant. This is the only place I died during this quest.\
\
Servants of Razelikh are level 57:\
\
Around the rim of the cliff near the Dark Portal 58,50\
Surrounding mobs are level 55 and rove in pairs.\
\
Watch the rovers movement path to determine best place to attack the servant at. Looking at the map, the 3rd servant from the right hand end has rovers that come very near his crystal.\
(Note: I have only been able to find 7 of the 9 so you may have to wait for two respawns.)",
    "268112036550120362006/12/09 08:45:55KarakenPosting for those of you who don't have UIs.\
\
The servants of Razelikh are found around the dark portal. Watch out for the Felguard patrol around the portal.\
\
Servants of Allistarj are all found along the eastern wall of the zone, stopping just before Nethergrade Keep.\
\
Servants of Servine are found along the wall north of the entrance to the tainted scar (which is the western wall)\
\
Servants of Grol are the most difficult to find, in my opinion. You can find one in a cave guarded by ogres in the mountain off the path to the tainted scar. Just follow the path until you begin travelling west, then go north and look for a lone mountain, Once you find ogres, you've found the one servant. The other place to find them are Grol's fort, located in the northwest corner of the zone. You'll know you found it because you'll see a tower and a base with horde banners. The servants are in there. To get there, go west along the northern wall from the entrance of the zone.\
\
A note that the servants will NOT die until you smash the crystal, and the stun effect on them wears off after around 30 seconds. If you're having trouble smashing the crystal, remember that you have to stun it (Drop around 85% of it's health) next to the crystal in order to smash it.\
\
For those who want coords, 49.7, 43.8 is where the lone Servant Of Grol is.The dark portal is around 58.8, 51.6. Frydebo provided coords to the other servents, as well as the Grol fort.\
\
Happy hunting!",
