    "76314551521442822007/03/03 10:41:10MorvranI completed mine the same day and it appeared to be working fine.  Two of us got our Dreadsteed.",
    "76312704630270462007/01/29 10:16:55ddc0660I'm not 100%, but when I finished this our party didn't outlast the waves of demons. We wiped. There were mobs still left in the circle. In desperation, the priest and pally (both soulstoned) resurrected to fight but when they did so the mobs despawned. The ritual _either_ finishes on itself despite dying or we were so close we just wiped as it ended. We then continued the ritual and killed the dreadsteed and master.\
\
My point? Don't give up if you wipe. If you've got a soulstone up (which you should) and you wipe, wait it out for a few minutes and then pop up.\
\
I didn't find this to be as easy as many other comments made it out to be. You can't waltz through Dire Maul even post-expansion.",
