    "7631800311080032006/12/06 22:13:17Leah0509Make sure to bring plenty of shards with you if you are the one keeping the bell wheel and candle up, each time you use the black loadstone it consumes a shard. Whenever I have done this quest it has generally taken between 10 and 15 shards\
