    "491801921120792007/11/06 17:25:18NinjaPirateTakiI came across chests very near the corn and rye and each had a single truesilver bar in them.  It's possible that the chests that spawn in these areas have a greater chance of spawning truesilver bars, though it could just be a huge coincidence.",
    "49845122120792007/05/17 10:39:33NaenthosYou must've been lucky because that's definitely not intended (with the chest containing truesilver). When I got there there was no chest at that location.",
    "491214993120792007/07/16 08:38:22HerishefChest spawns are not guaranteed.. every spawn location is linked to another 2 to 4 other possible locations nearby..\
\
