If you need more Scorched Ectoplasm from Silithus, there is a little house inside Southwind Village at (62.7,49.7) which has 7 mobs in it.",
    "89241761381156442006/12/20 12:45:51GattamIn Winterspring, there is a long building at the SE corner of the lake. If you set up your distiller at the lake end of the building, you should be able to pull 6-8 ghosts to the distiller before it runs out. Should be able to get your 12 with 2 fuels.\
