    "3882138121101381212007/08/15 01:23:01jleaheyI'm a lvl 49 Lock and have found that it is much safer to reach places by staying close to the outside mtns when you travel. Rather than runnung/riding straight thru the middle. I used my VW to divert attention away from me then ran in and got the bones. If I got killed I just ran back and rezzed right next to the bones. Pick just the right time to rez and you can get 1-2 each trip. It means alot of running due to getting killed several times but I completed the quest in about 20-30 minutes.",
