    "604162626201626262007/10/04 01:52:58SwampianYeah right, if you have a lousy patience, do not try to do this quest now. the Charts appearing seems about the same category with an angel landing on the top of Big Ben, meaning, maybe sometimes has happened, but seems impossible. I have tried to destroy the orders, abandon and retake the quest etc etc and no goddamn charts anywhere. always the orders. This sucks.",
    "60450506050502006/11/28 19:03:19TheOnyxOn the southern shore of Stranglethorn Vale, you'll find two Bloodsail camps and a rowboat. The charts and orders can spawn in either of the camps or on the rowboat. The Swashbucklers will be all around along the southern shore.",
    "608189690101896902007/11/22 22:49:12truhordeall coords confirmed found the riddle at about on top of a barrel on the west most ship lvl 2 i think at around 29,89\
