    "60819898120198982007/01/09 07:38:11snuffedDon't forget to look for the riddle that starts this quest: http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=624 while you're on the ships; you'll usually find it on the ship that has Captain Stillwater on it - the one that is by itself apart from the other 2 ships (though I'm not too sure if it spawns on the other ships, but my friends told me they also got it the same ship, so... =)",
