    "7737810204159022007/05/10 17:33:58modsquadJust mail them to an alt, if you don't have an alt, make some mules for storing stuff, mail it to them, it stays for 30 days then gets sent back to you. Lots of storage space if you are creative.",
    "773759027059022006/12/05 08:42:17rlyehThe residue only drops from mobs in BRD, but if nobody else in your group is running for Thorium B rep, then you can amass a large amount of this stuff in no time at all.\
