    "7737203469102034692007/12/18 15:50:24XLiuhuJust got to 0/12000 Honored a minute ago. I just wanted to come here and tell you guys that it took me about 5 minutes and 42 seconds to spam the npc for returning these. Here's how to do it if you have all the 960 (as mentioned above) residues:\
\
1. Get an addon that has an \"auto-complete quest\" feature (you just need to click the quest name and it clicks \"Complete quest\" for you automatically).\
2. Zoom your camera all the way in to 1st person view (could be done without zooming if postioned right I guess, but I did it like this).\
3. Walk next to the NPC and position the camera right, so you can click both the NPC and the quest name in the gossip window without moving your mouse.\
4. Right-click the NPC so the gossip window opens, then left-click the quest name and the addon completes it for you.\
5. Repeat step 4 unti Honored. :)\
\
