    "580316055npcAlchemist Arbington11056npcAlchemist Arbington1105649501553325537355384580155803",
    "5803207353102073532007/12/26 02:23:11shadowolf86Confirmed. Just beat the crap out of him as a solo level 62 prot pallie. He is still elite as of 2.3, although the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=12650]Attuned Dampener[/url] used to help kill him has been greatly upgraded. First off, make sure you do the prequest, [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=4972]Counting Out Time[/url], before you fight him, in order to get the Attuned Dampener. Using that will make him much easier.\
\
Second, make sure you come into Andorhal through Sorrow Hill and over the bridge. Clear the area of solo mobs, and watch out for the Flesh Reapers on patrol, they're elites. It's a good idea to kill any of those in the immediate area. \
\
Now start [i]carefully[/i] pulling mobs from around Araj. You can pull not only the first group in front of him, but also the 2 spectral ghosts behind them, and if you go around to the side, the scorching ghouls and skeletal warlords as well. It isn't difficult at all to completely clear the area around him.\
\
After he's clear, stand about 10 yards away and use the Attuned Dampener. From there on, keep yourself healed and he's cake. Pallies should know what to drop on him. Consecration, Exorcism, etc. Keep a mana potion handy just in case.\
\
At any rate, rumors of his difficulty are greatly exaggerated.",
    "580348374048372006/11/27 13:20:42rlyehIt is possible to kill Araj and loot the scarab before all of her guards are downed.  If you have a hunter or mages in your group the crowd control for the guards should be okay.  \
\
You will need to separate Araj from the mass of guards and hack it up.  Most of the time i've seen a hunter pull her away while mages frost/slow the guards.   A VW aoe taunt is also nice to keep the guards focused while Araj is taken down. \
\
If you kill Araj but die in the process you can easily run back, res yourself, and loot araj for scarab before respawn.",
