    "551527203027202006/11/03 22:44:06atfghosthunterThe clones are actually immune only to AoE. The best way to handle them with healers in mind is to have everyone use an auto-attack and just right click them (wand for casters). You can eliminate enough of them such that everyone but a priest or healer can turn back a focus on Jandice, and easily finish them.",
    "551527106126352006/11/03 16:31:15TheOnyxActually, the V-target thing was apparently fixed. The best way to handle the clones now is to hit the button on your keyboard that targets the last hostile creature (default is 'g'). Alternatively, you can use a macro to target Jandice.",
    "55156186230618622007/04/04 05:16:45lsub300If you bring a hunter this is the time to use his/hers pet. It will not loose focus on the real Jandice.\
