    "5862145316301453162007/08/28 07:02:03KeilunI ran this on my Draenei Paladin last night. I don't know if they changed this quest at all or not (bug maybe), but it appears that if you have your disguise still up when Taelan dies, the quest will fail. This happened twice for me. On the third try, I dropped my disguise when Isillien approached him stood back a bit to stay out of aggro range and the event went on normally.\
