    "8234140203101402032007/08/18 16:56:31MikalOne thing to note is that this quest does not apply to a SPECIFIC shaman, but ANY shaman in general. If it's a \"Timbermaw Shaman\" it may have it. However, be forewarned that if someone has come through the area previously, and picked the shaman's pocket, and it has not been killed, it won't have anything (though it refills its pockets in about five minutes.)\
