    "8234122415211223132007/07/17 19:59:43NazgrolKill the Deadwood furbolgs southwest of Timbermaw Hold in northwestern Felwood to fix rep.",
    "82349047550904752007/05/25 17:41:02raventreeGot this quest at lvl 50, and completed it at lvl 50. I have no rep with Timbermaw Hold - I just stealthed and pickpocketed. I am combat spec, but I have maxed out MoD and Camo, so that helped with sneaking past the mobs undetected, I'm sure. \
\
At 44,26 like krisdl said above, and 48.4,28.2 are lots of Timbermaw Shamans. They are in Ursolan, which is slightly northeast of the Timbermaw Hold gate. I distracted, pickpocketed, and the Sealed Azure Bag dropped on the first try. \
\
