    "7043203279702032792007/12/18 08:08:36adashielYour impression of this quest depends on when you do it.  If you're with the crowd that tries to get it done on day 1 of Winter Veil, chances are you'll be camping out in Alterac for awhile.  It can be frustrating.  After a few days, however, things will ease up for the poor Greench.  Before his inevitable gankage, he'll breathe in a little of that clean mountain air, maybe scratch the itch that's been bothering him for the last ten spawns.  By the midpoint of the holiday, he'll have enough time to play some pinochle, and maybe even a game or two of Monopoly.\
