    "667176534101765342007/10/29 18:50:53samedhi13I accepted the quest and manned the cannon. No Nagas came. Fired several shots, no Naga still. Abandoned quest. The Captain vanished and Naga arrived. Killed them, exited game, reloaded. Captain back in place, re-accepted quest, manned cannons, Nagas appeared . Boom dead repeat x 3 quest completed job done",
