    "667518921051892006/11/29 20:34:53cmkennedyThis quest is ludicrously easy.  It can be performed at the lowest possible level.  Three waves of Naga appear from behind the hill.  One wave of three, one wave of two, and a final wave of three.  They are all level 40.\
