    "975162936311628862007/10/04 16:09:54TiranE'kos are found in Winterspring only. Any Jujus you make can be used anywhere of course.",
    "975151394801513942007/09/10 19:37:05MothmanTo add to diesilgirl's comment:\
Juju Power can be made from the Winterfall E'ko which drop off the various Winterfall furbolgs.\
Juju Might can be made from the Frostmaul E'ko which drop off Frostmaul giants and preservers down south. Be aware, they are elites.\
Juju Flurry can be made from the  Frostsaber E'ko which drop from the various Frostsabres, stalkers, huntresses, cubs, etc, up north.\
\
These three Juju are classed as \"Battle Elixirs\" and wont stack with each other or other  Battle Elixirs.\
\
Juju Guile can be made from the Wildkin E'ko which drop off the various Owlbeasts in the surrounding area.\
Juju Escape can be made from the Ice Thistle E'ko which drop off the various Ice Thistle Yetis in the surrounding area.\
Juju Ember can be made from the Shardtooth E'ko which drop off the various Shardtooth maulers and bears.\
Juju Chill can be made from the Chillwind E'ko which drop off the various flyers in the area. Fledgling Chillwinds, Ravagers and Chimaeras.\
\
As above, These four Juju fall under the \"Guardian Elixir\" category and wont stack with each other or other Guardians.",
