    "4123125827201258272007/07/24 02:41:51czeanoThe Heart of the Mountain is completely unrelated to the Dark Coffer (described above), but their proximity causes much confusion.  Both are located in the vault in Blackrock Depths and both involve a summoned boss event to open.\
