    "71411719031143512006/12/19 02:12:42CaffiTo start this quest, go talk to the female dwarf near the tent to the east of the cave entrance, north from southshore.\
\
At level 51 (Lowest possible level for the quest) You may be able to slay a few hordies in the battleground, but i advice you to stay away from the bosses in the keep and the big towers, because their \"aoe\" attacks (just like a warrior's cleave) is able to deal enough damage to take out a level 60 with 6000 armor in only 3-5 hits.\
You need a lot of armor and at least 1 dedicated healer to survive these guys.\
\
As for the quest; Drek'thar himself is in the big horde keep in the frostwolf camp in the very south of the battleground. Normal gameplay lets the alliance take the frostwolf relief hut, then 10-15 enters and attacks Drek'thar.\
I am not sure if you get the kill by simply being in the battleground (Staying in the first alliance base) But i do know that you dont actually have to attack Drek'thar yourself. Healing, helping, or just simply being near it is more then enough.\
I died once while we were killing him, and i am not sure if i was in range for the kill, but i did get the quest done.",
    "71411435130143512006/12/12 17:55:25SolarFusionOnce you complete this quest by talking to Prospector Stonehewer, you will be able to continue on. Talk to her once again after completion and you will be able to choose 4 great items.\
