    "1560139981111356102007/08/18 08:42:40BaybansYou are correct if someone is doing the quest Tooga will not be found... after all he is busy heading home right? His location can be one of two places as far as I'm aware, I found him 29,60 and later 31,74. The end location is also spot on. 66,25.",
    "15607130920713092007/04/22 23:01:44auiotourTooga Can also be found at  29,60",
    "1560212591102125912008/01/04 03:20:50MoonLite[u]Tooga follows YOU[/u], you don't have to follow him. He walks at around 110% speed, so running with a steed might get him lost. \
He attracts almost no aggro and if you take care where you walk you can walk all the way without fighting a single mob.\
You have 30 minutes, but can do it in 10-15 minutes if you avoid fights.\
(druids can use [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=8955]Soothe Animal[/url], to avoid more fights)\
(hunters can use track beasts/humanoids to manouvre between mobs more easily)\
\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=5955]Tooga[/url] is found between (29,60)-(30,73) , around Thistleshrub Valley. You might have to wait for him to respawn. \
He doesn't roam much, mostly stays at the same spot. \
\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=6015]Torta[/url] is at (66,25) , just south of the Steemwheedle Port in the north east. She's always there so no waiting there. \
\
Mobs neer Tooga are lvl48-49 elementals. \
Mobs go down from lvl48 to lvl40ish in the north (scorpids/wolves/basilisks/pirates).\
\
If you arrive, Tooga's gonna have some words with his wife: \
[ul]\
[li]Tooga: Torta, my love! I have returned at long last. [/li]\
[li]Torta: You have any idea how long I've been waiting here? And where's dinner? All that time gone and nothing to show for it? [/li]\
[li]Tooga: My dearest Torta, I have been gone for so long. Finally we are reunited. At long last our love van blossom again. [/li]\
[li]Torta: Enough with the rambling. I am starving! Now, get your dusty shell into that ocean and bring momma some grub. [/li]\
[li]Tooga: Yes, torta. Whatever your heart desires... [/li]\
[li]Torta: And try not to get lost this time...[/li]\
Tooga walks to the sea and disappears...\
[/ul]",
