  ["The Scrimshank Redemption48"] = {
    "1014839npcSenior Surveyor Fizzledowser7724npcSenior Surveyor Fizzledowser77244400Gadgetzan25011021103113432",
    "10208790202087902007/12/28 14:15:56KuzazieA lot of people would think that actually FINDING the guy would be the worst part of this quest. . . Well, I think that going to this CREEPY place is the worst part!! Well, anyway. . . Well, The Gapping Chasm is pretty much in the bottom Southeast corner of Tanaris, Southeast of Dunemaul Compound and South of Broken Pillar. Scrimshank's Surveying Gear is in what many people are calling it, \"The Spiral.\" Looking at the map, the spiral (in The Gapping Chasm,) is the thing with a curved line by it, which is on the most Eastern part of the Gapping Chasm. There are level 37-39 creeping alien dudes here, making this a little tricky, but being a 49 druid, I could just prowl to it. Once you enter the Spiral, there is a narrow tunnel, with different parts branching off from it. Take your first left. Proceed through the tunnel with caution, 'cause there's still alien dudes in here. Go to the end of that  the tunnel, and then take the only other tunnel that has been untraveled (the tunnel you didn't come in through) in this little room. After a few seconds of traveling through this tunnel, there's a fork in the road. Take the left, (Man, you have to take left A LOT!!!,) and then you enter a REALLY WEIRD ROOM, and after taking a few steps into this room, turn left. Travel down that tiny little part of the room and there's the Surveying Gear. It takes a while, but hey, you get 6300experience and 250 rep. with Gadgetzan!",
    "108730240873022007/05/22 08:21:58orgustusquest location 55,71 solo easy with level 47 hunter just use feigh death and intimidation. might want to set hearthstone to gadgetzan if possible so you dont have to fight your way back out as they will all be respawned by the time your done also quest is quite some distance away. for some reason i found it alot harder to get out.",
    "103893152038932006/11/19 20:16:31LiriGo to the Gaping Chasm (56, 61), find the entrance spiraling down at (55, 70). Take the 2nd tunnel you see when going down the spiral, the one going north. Inside the tunnel at the first fork go right. Then go through the circular room.\
\
After the circular room at the first fork go right. You will enter a large room. The Scrimshank's Surveying Gear (55, 71) is at the western side of the room.\
\
Given the swarmers I would suggest a druid/paladin/Un'Goro crystal to damage attackers or some EZ throw Dynamite.\
\
=Sera Vala on Earthen Ring=",
