    "1018467121818422007/11/14 21:48:02KhamoraWhile it is easy as a feral druid, you still have to watch for the roaming bugs because the tunnels you will enter are very tight and there aren't ways to go around the roaming bugs, they all stopped and looked at me as a 49 feral, one ended up discovering me and brought a friend.  Best advice for a stealthing/prowling individual is to wait for a wandering bug to *leave* the tunnel you are going into.  On your way back, do the same thing or you may be stepped on and aggro another 1 - 2 bugs.",
