    "77017443620744362007/04/28 13:45:40KaenaI had trouble finding this myself so I thought I'd be specific. \
\
He can be found inside a cave called the Slag Pit. It's the second cave from the left. Once inside work your way in and turn left when you see a gate. There will be a winding ramp up and soon enough you'll see a balcony with Overseer Maltorius and his adds. It's at about 40,36, don't mistake this co-ordinate for the same area above ground.\
\
When I did this quest I found a rare spawn but he's pretty easy to take down so I took him down first. There are two ways to go about doing this, one is to keep them scattered and focus dps on one, and the other is to use a form of CC and focus dps on one. I would recommend taking out each of the two guards before moving on to the Overseer as he has about 14,000HP and hits pretty hard. \
\
Behind him is the plans for the quest \"What the Flux?\". If you're just after that you could fear them all, run in, get the plans and jump out.",
