    "7701190406101904062007/11/24 11:58:25PhoenixAshActually, and this might have changed with the patch, Maltorius is lvl 50 but not Elite. And he only has one Bodyguard who is lvl 48 and not Elite either. But he does cast the nasty shadow spells mentioned before. However, I soloed this as a lvl 47 hunter without breaking a sweat.",
    "770110626721962912007/06/18 00:47:30tzireanThis is how I soloed it, as well.  Mind controlled Overseer Maltorius, spent all his mana shadowbolting his adds, but made sure not to kill either one.  When he hit 3% (one add was about the same, the other around 35%), I broke the mind control, mind blasted him for the kill, and feared.  Looted his head, looted the plans, and finished off the adds.",
    "77019471810947182007/05/31 12:32:05BordanisThe easiest way to find him: go to 48-44 on left side of tower, then drop down go in to tunnel, veer to the left and there he is. He hits pretty hard and uses polymorph. Did this quest with 56 pally and 54 warrior and was still tough. With a good dps and healer shouldnt be too much of a problem.",
