    "448359879170598792007/03/30 20:52:21zaberIf you are level 70 you can do this solo even without stealth.  Helps to be a mage to blink past a few \"tight spots\".\
\
Enter BRD, go through the locked door on your left, continue straight to the \"highway\", take a right and follow the hall to Incendius, melt his face, loot corpse, dance happy jig, disenchant BOP drop (if you can), continue straight and go up the ramp, avoid mobs by walking on the railing most fo the way.  At the top fo the ramp go through the doorway and go to the left, take the next left into the Cofffer Room.  Blink past the boss and the dog so you are standing against the Dark Coffer.  Attack and kill the dog and ignore the boss until the dog is dead.  At level 70 you should resist all or most of the bosses spells.  Kill the boss, loot and dance again, DE, walk to the edge of the room (stand about where the boss was standing), adjust your camera angle so you can click the picture on the wall and read the caption n the picture to find where the NPC is that you need to kill to get the Dark Coffer Key.  Backtrack to wherever that mobs is and kill him to get the key, then return to the Coffer Room, open the Dark Coffer, loot contents, hearth out to Orgrimmar or Ironforge... spam the trade channel til you sell the \"enchant\" or get ignored by everyone on your server.\
\
If you happen to get ignored by everyone on the server, pay Blizzard to do a server transfer to another.  Repeat as needed.\
\
:-P",
