    "13806606780660672007/04/12 13:20:03DignamI completed this quest solo as a level 44 priest. The first two waves were easy: I simply killed the first wave incredibly fast and had a quick time interval to drink before the second wave spawned. When the second wave came, I nuked the healer while the other two were feared. The last wave I simply tab-mind soothed all the mobs, and then I mindcontrolled Khan Hratha. As you can imagine, killing the 3 ads was easy using him: he has a cleave ability that deals massive damage. After the three ads were dead, he was at about 50% and I killed him easily. Good luck!",
