    "13803275050327502007/02/08 16:20:14BinaryBurnoutSoloed as a level 41 Warrior. Was not an easy quest to complete solo though. The horn was relatively easy, just low drop rate. Although the boss proved to be difficult. Died twice during boss fight, finally used retal + death wish + blood fury and ended up with 130hp.\
