    "13806027050602702007/03/31 19:35:25orionisAs a level 41 Prot Paly, I adapted this hunter's strat... sorta. The waves were easy. Blocked them to death. No big deal. Plenty of time to drink between waves even. The last wave, I killed the healer and one of his guards, bubbled and healed up a bit... killed the other guard... started meleeing him. Had to use a Mana Potion. Stunned him... Holy Light... start again... did a Blessing of Protection after my recently bubbled debuff was gone and first aided up a bit... stunned him again and meleed him down. Used Seals and Judgements of Light and Wisdom.",
