    "630209678102096782007/12/30 03:04:38PhaithAs of patch 2.3 all the mobs are lvl 41-42 & King Mukla is a lvl 42 non elite, so I was able to solo as shadow preist easily lvl 45. The only problem is you still cant actually get the quest until 45.",
