    "924810872321125262007/06/21 14:23:34maximusprimeSince TBC came out, everyone goes to Outland at 58.  This quest was designed pre-TBC for level 60 players who could no longer gain experience.  I assume that Blizzard knows this, as well as the fact that Silithus is rarely visited nowdays (as are the old 60 dungeons/raids like Onyx, Naxx, Strat, Scholo, AQ20/40, ZG, BWL, and MC).  \
