[li]27:34 Entrance - Guarded by a Ghoul 58 Elite ~17000HP - Detects Stealth - Stationary Mob[/li]\
[li]24:25 Entrance - Guarded by a Ghoul 58 Elite ~17000HP - Detects Stealth - Stationary Mob[/li]\
