    "294618112110181122006/12/27 16:19:28SybaekThis is probably the easiest 15k xp and 5g you will ever make this game.  You head to Uldum in the very southern part of Tanaris.  You can't miss it, there are lvl 48-50 elite giants standing around.  There is a path from the left that you can follow and reach the pedestal without aggroing any of them.  You access the pedestal and a hologram appears.  bam 4700xp.  Talk to the hologram, but take care not to get ambushed by the patrolling elite (your screen while shake when he is near you).  After talking with the hologram, access the pedestal again, bam another 4700xp.  Hearth--portal--walk to IF again and speak with the guy in the Hall of Explorers.  You'll get some gold and 450xp.  Accept the next quest and walk over to another guy about 200 yards away, bam another 4700 xp and some more gold.\
